precis:
Order which (a) revokes Order in Council P.C. 1990-2072, and (b) enacts
the PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1992, NO. 4, which
prohibits prospecting and mining on certain lands situated in the Yukon
in order to facilitate the settlement of territorial claims made by the
CHAMPAGNE/AISHIHIK FIRST NATION.
